# 🎯 Vision

Build a deployable, provider-agnostic AI Platform that enables enterprise applications to add modern AI capabilities without implementing AI infrastructure themselves.

The platform should expose reusable APIs for:

* Project Management
* Connectors & Ingestion
* Storage
* OCR & Parsing
* Chunking
* Embeddings
* Vector Search & Hybrid Retrieval
* Chat
* Voice
* Evaluation
* Observability
* Agent Workflows

Applications interact only with the platform APIs while the platform manages the complete AI lifecycle internally.

