# 🧠 Learning Philosophy

This project is learning-first.

Every major feature should explain:

* Why it exists
* How it works
* Internal request flow
* Architecture
* Trade-offs
* Production considerations
* Alternatives
* Common implementation mistakes

Understanding the engineering principles is considered as important as implementing the feature itself.

