## Repository layout

```text
backend/app/
  models/       All ORM entities (shared; registered in composition/orm_registry.py)
  composition/  ORM registry + Alembic migrations
  api/          HTTP composition (routes + router mounting)
  dependencies/ FastAPI DI (composition only — modules must not import)
  core/         Cross-cutting kernel
  platform/     Shared infrastructure (db, persistence, domain helpers, http, jobs)
  modules/      Feature slices (services, repositories, schemas only)
```

